Activity 3. HTML and CSS
1.	Being a web developer and having a portfolio helps a lot while applying for opportunities and acts as a showcase. In this activity, build your own personal website using HTML and CSS. On your page include or all of the following information:
•	Homepage 
	Your name
	A description of yourself in two sentences or less. Emphasize the most important word(s).
	Social media links
•	About page(Short description about yourself, Details: Name, Age, location). 
•	Skills page
•	Projects page
•	Contact page